                    SIMPLE INSTALLATION STEPS

1.  In the CBTXREF exec, look for string:

      parse value keywd( "ISPTLIB" )

    and change the dataset name to your ISPTLIB library that you
    want to use.  Change that name as well, in the job $COPEXEC.

2.  After making sure that the dataset names are correct, run the
    job:  $COPEXEC

3.  Execute the exec:  %CBTXREF

4.  We are not talking about renewing the table here.  We are only
    dealing with the table as shipped with the package.

